In the future for these kinds of problems, implement the correlate function yourself since it is the core of this problem. 
Also be sure to label the axes and title of the graph including the names of the wav files (-3)  
For the snare detection, you should not have hardcoded the values of each snare hit. Every value > 150 may have worked for these files but will not always carry over (-1). 
All your snare locations are off by one because the snare recording does not begin at sample zero. It begins at 1 (Does not account for lag). (-1)
